gomodel:SYNGO_4800  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 1B: superresolution microscopy (3D-STORM) showed that Celsr3 colocalized with both presynaptic marker Bassoon and postsynaptic marker PSD-95.\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected. As also depicted by authors in Figure 1C.. Experimental description: M&M: \"Hippocampi were dissected from E18.5 mice, and hippocampal neuron culture was performed as previously described\"\n\nantibody:\nrabbit anti-Celsr3 (generated in the Zou laboratory)" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099059 replaced by GO:0048787" ;
